p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">One reason Johnson is even in conte=
ntion for the speakership is that Republicans held on to seats like Lawler=
=E2=80=99s. Even so,
Johnson has a nearly impossible margin. Kentucky conservative iconoclast <s=
trong>Thomas Massie</strong> has already stated he will not vote for Johnso=
