y think are going to be important in a meeting with their clients, but neve=
r are. There was talk of A.I. replacing junior bankers, but I haven=E2=80=
=99t heard any examples of that yet. That doesn=E2=80=99t mean it won=E2=80=
=99t happen as A.I. gets smarter, better, and more accurate. But you=E2=80=
